4
00:02:10,250 --> 00:02:11,625
I GOT THIRSTY.

5
00:02:11,708 --> 00:02:13,916
- Mother: OF COURSE, DEAR.
JUST HOLD ON FOR ONE MINUTE.

6
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,833
HERE.
- Child: YAY.

7
